      "/news/architecting-the-future": {
        "published": true,
        "body": "<p>Michael Ben Eli discusses the renaissance of the concept of \"design\" and how all aspects of human activity are manifestations of a design process and what that implies about our role as human beings on the planet.</p>\r\n<iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/12808820?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=ffffff\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n<p>On June 3, 2010, the Buckminster Fuller Institute hosted \"Architecting the Future\" a day long gathering, as part of the 2010 Buckminster Fuller Challenge events in Washington DC.</p>",
